379
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:49,380
Maybe you murdered your husband

380
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:51,580
and then

381
00:17:51,860 --> 00:17:52,860
blamed it

382
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:54,220
