534
00:23:27,320 --> 00:23:28,060
and talk nonsense.

535
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:29,260
Sir.

536
00:23:30,100 --> 00:23:31,180
Calm down.

537
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:32,420
Give me a few days.

